msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:12
msgid "Drivers"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:15
msgid "Windows"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:18
msgid ""
"Windows Vista, Windows 7 and Windows 8 are supported. You can download the "
"latest drivers and firmware from "
"https://support.alphatheta.com/products/4416565750809."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:21
msgid ""
"If you're using Windows and have problems getting both sound outputs to work"
" properly, please try using a different Sound {term}`API` in the "
"{ref}`preferences <preferences-sound-api>`. DirectSound seems to have issues"
" with this controller. WASAPI seems to work fine, as does MME, although only"
" with higher latencies. On Windows 10, only MME works."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:26
msgid "Mac OS X & Linux"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:29
msgid "You don’t need any drivers on Mac OS X and Linux."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:31
msgid "The controller supports Mac OS X 10.6 and up."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:33
msgid "Usage"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:36
msgid "Library browsing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:39
msgid ""
"The controls for library browsing can be found in the center top of the "
"controller."
msgstr ""

