msgid "1/16th beat loop roll"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:20
msgid "1/8th beat loop roll"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:20
msgid "1/4th beat loop roll"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:20
msgid "1/2 beat loop roll"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:20
msgid "1 beat loop roll"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:20
msgid "2 beat loop roll"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:20
msgid "4 beat loop roll"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:20
msgid "8 beat loop roll"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:166
msgid "Pads - kill (shift + manual loop)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:169
msgid ""
"By pressing the manual loop button while holding shift (it should start "
"blinking) you can make the pads behave as kill switches."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:20
msgid "Kill low"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:20
msgid "Kill mid"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:20
msgid "Kill high"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:20
msgid "Mute"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:179
msgid "Effects"
msgstr "效果"

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:182
msgid "Over the jogwheels there are sections allowing to control effects."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:184
msgid "Turning the knobs will control the wet/dryness of an effect."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:186
msgid ""
"Turning the knobs while holding one of the three FX buttons will control the"
" first, second or third parameter of an effect, respectively."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:188
msgid ""
"If holding shift when using the knobs the “super” parameter can be "
"controlled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:190
msgid ""
"Pressing the central FX button (number 2) while holding shift will toggle "
"the effect for the headphones, while the left and right buttons (number 1 "
"and 3) will toggle the effect for the active deck in the left and right "
"sides of the controller respectively."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:193
msgid ""
"You can choose between effects by entering “kill mode” and using pads 1 and "
"2 while holding shift."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:195
msgid "Channel fader start"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb.md:198
msgid ""
"By moving a channel fader up from the very bottom while holding shift when a"
" deck is paused, the deck will start playing. Moving the fader back to the "
"bottom without releasing shift stops the deck and moves it back to its "
"original position."
msgstr ""
